=================================
=  README for ex5 - crosswords  =
=================================


==================
=  Description:  =
==================
crossword.py - searches a 2d crossword for words in a file given by the user.
outputs the found words with a number each appears into a file defined by user.

crossword3d.py - searches a 3d crossword for words given
by the user, in the directions given by the user. outputs the
words found and the number of times they appear into a file defined by user.
searches using function from crossword.py.



